# Enterprise Task Management Backend Project

## Overview

Build a production-ready enterprise backend system for task management using Quarkus or Spring Boot.

The system allows users to assign tasks to other users, track task progress, send notifications via email, and process asynchronous events using RabbitMQ and Kafka.

---

# Core Technologies

## Backend
- Java 21
- Quarkus (recommended) or Spring Boot

## Database
- PostgreSQL

## Messaging
- RabbitMQ
- Kafka

## Security
- Google OAuth2 Login
- JWT Authentication

## Infrastructure
- Docker Compose

## Additional
- Flyway Migration
- Mail Service
- Scheduler
- REST API
- Clean Architecture
- DTO + Mapper Pattern

